        <detaileddescription>
<para>If Strong makes additional efforts to avoid creating multiple edges, in some rare cases it is not possible (cases with extremely bad topology), if you faced one try to use <ref refid="group__MeshFixerGroup_1ga9f1f866643e15bf1b9d9131f2d6dad0e" kindref="member">MR::duplicateMultiHoleVertices</ref> before <ref refid="group__FillHoleGroup_1gaea109869817edaf2a249691f0ec7f1bb" kindref="member">MR::fillHole</ref></para>
<para>If Simple avoid creating edges that already exist in topology (default)</para>
<para>If None do not avoid multiple edges </para>
